com.aylanetworks.aylasdk

类 AylaDSManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.aylanetworks.aylasdk.AylaDSManager
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    AylaConnectivity.AylaConnectivityListener, AylaDeviceManager.DeviceManagerListener, WebSocket.WebSocketConnectionObserver

    public class AylaDSManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements WebSocket.WebSocketConnectionObserver, AylaDeviceManager.DeviceManagerListener, AylaConnectivity.AylaConnectivityListener
    The AylaDSManager is an internal SDK component used to keep devices updated using the Device Stream service of Ayla Networks.

      • deviceManagerInitComplete

        public void deviceManagerInitComplete(java.util.Map<java.lang.String,AylaError> deviceFailures)
        从接口复制的说明: AylaDeviceManager.DeviceManagerListener
        Called when the device manager has completed initialization. When this method is called, the device manager has the complete set of devices and their properties available.
        指定者:
        deviceManagerInitComplete 在接口中 AylaDeviceManager.DeviceManagerListener
        参数:
        deviceFailures - A map of DSNs of devices that failed to be initialized to the specific error that caused initialization failure. If a device's properties were not available, or details could not be fetched about a particular device, the DSN of that device will be included deviceFailures map.

        If all devices could be initialized, the deviceFailures map will be empty.

      • deviceManagerInitFailure

        public void deviceManagerInitFailure(AylaError error,
                                     AylaDeviceManager.DeviceManagerState failureState)
        从接口复制的说明: AylaDeviceManager.DeviceManagerListener
        Called when the DeviceManager could not complete initialization. This usually occurs when the DeviceManager is unable to fetch the list of devices from the cloud and does not have the device list cached.

        The DeviceManager will be in the Error state when this notification is received. The state the DeviceManager was in when the failure occurred will be passed via the failureState argument to this method.

        指定者:
        deviceManagerInitFailure 在接口中 AylaDeviceManager.DeviceManagerListener
        参数:
        error - Error that occurred
        failureState - State of the device manager when the error occurred

        public void deviceListChanged(ListChange change)
        从接口复制的说明: AylaDeviceManager.DeviceManagerListener
        Called whenever the list of devices has changed. The change object can be queried to find the DSNs of the devices that were added or removed from the device list.
        指定者:
        deviceListChanged 在接口中 AylaDeviceManager.DeviceManagerListener
        参数:
        change - The ListChange object containing information about the devices that were added or removed.
